    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Thanks for the overtime</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;After Tasks” is a horror game in which you experience a special kind of work done at school.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The work is simple. All you have to do is to play the video and wait until it finishes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play the video, solve the phenomenon, find the best solution according to the situation, and complete the job.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121090/extras/73507751f88cd54bcd6632792e119aec.poster.avif?t=1730386896\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121090/extras/73507751f88cd54bcd6632792e119aec.webm?t=1730386896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121090/extras/73507751f88cd54bcd6632792e119aec.mp4?t=1730386896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Don't worry, we have a manual</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our work is very varied. But don't worry, we have prepared a manual for this purpose.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Most of the information is in the manual. Please do not miss any information.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please be careful not to be confused by the large amount of information in the manual.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121090/extras/0334889c67c3445d505dc42b73c8f6e8.poster.avif?t=1730386896\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121090/extras/0334889c67c3445d505dc42b73c8f6e8.webm?t=1730386896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121090/extras/0334889c67c3445d505dc42b73c8f6e8.mp4?t=1730386896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Please don't do that. It's obstruction of business</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Various phenomena that occur within the school can affect video playback.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When dealing with them, please implement the appropriate solution for each phenomenon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Also, watch out for the invisible “them”. They will target you relentlessly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121090/extras/ade03ecdee4e8e5453ca1a7898bd5583.poster.avif?t=1730386896\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121090/extras/ade03ecdee4e8e5453ca1a7898bd5583.webm?t=1730386896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121090/extras/ade03ecdee4e8e5453ca1a7898bd5583.mp4?t=1730386896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Strange things for strange things</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sometimes a Amulet is needed to deal with paranormal phenomena.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Amulet should be written on the spot, attached to the object, and taken to the TV after it is resolved.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121090/extras/549cf39d11809a35f4519df20a2d2ad9.poster.avif?t=1730386896\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121090/extras/549cf39d11809a35f4519df20a2d2ad9.webm?t=1730386896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121090/extras/549cf39d11809a35f4519df20a2d2ad9.mp4?t=1730386896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >I hear these things are good these days</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some of the phenomena that occur in late night school can make business operations more meaningful.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If completed as additional work, they may help with overtime for the day.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121090/extras/a4ff5a276934cfd7cb8d94fb070759f1.poster.avif?t=1730386896\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121090/extras/a4ff5a276934cfd7cb8d94fb070759f1.webm?t=1730386896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121090/extras/a4ff5a276934cfd7cb8d94fb070759f1.mp4?t=1730386896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Estimated playing time : 3 ~ 4 hours</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Regarding the live video/streaming of this game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thank you for choosing this video for your live video/distribution.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To avoid unnecessary problems, please read the following guidelines.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Guidelines</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The following guidelines apply to the live video and distribution of this title, regardless of whether you are an individual or a corporation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&gt;Please include the title of the game in the title or summary section of the video or distribution.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&gt;Please include the URL link to the store page of this work in the video or video distribution summary.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&gt;Monetization by the functions provided by the platform you are using is permitted.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&gt;Please refrain from videos and distribution of content that is slanderous or offensive to public order and morals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&gt;We are not responsible for any problems that may occur as a result of posting or distributing videos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*The guidelines are subject to change without notice.</p>",
